Meta keys by type:
- `course` → `code` (string), `provider` (string), `due` (ISO date or human string)
- `event` → `date` (ISO date or human string), `location` (string)
- `person` → `role` (string), `affiliation` (string)
- `scholarship` → `amount` (string), `deadline` (ISO date or human string)

Aim for 5–8 items. Keep `title` under 80 characters, `why` under 140. Use lowercase-kebab
for `id` — downstream agents look items up by that id.
